{"type": "article", "id": 6970, "title": "MAGIC GRIP 魔法防滑陶瓷", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-02T07:39:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234144zqpZOacJV2m194Pw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t陶瓷餐具滑落跌碎，简直是家居生活的噩梦。这款餐具彻底解决了这个问题。在餐具底部加入无害硅胶，即能够防止餐具在叠加存放或移动时打滑，又可以减少餐具相互碰撞带来的噪音，同时也有利于保护餐具，高档餐桌和其他家具。而 MAGIC GRIP 采用的材料也适宜盛放食物，可遇水，可加热，并且在 180 °C 下保持稳定。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234142qbfo7ieSXlQZz8Dm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234143xRYOjX1KaD5rLvzQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"1.1787037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234143j1sFzUm5vIRn6OJX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}